data.description: Beautiful 3 Bedroom 2.5 Bath home in Sundance Square! ***Assumable FHA loan at 5%***This lovely 2-story features an open floor plan with a spacious living room, dining room that flows into the open island kitchen with stainless steel appliances and ample cabinetry for storage, all bedrooms upstairs including the primary bedroom with room for a sitting space/office nook and full bath, and loft family/game room. The backyard is ready for entertaining or relaxing, complete with a patio and large yard. Conveniently located nearby schools, shopping, loop 1604 and TX-211. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your next home. Book your personal tour today!
